  
  ACTULUS SECURITAS
  The main feature is that the ambient environmental conditions of a worker can be accessed by any other person
(instructor).The helmet is connected to the internet.
  It includes temperature and pulse sensors.A button is also provided, which on pressed sents an alert.The collected
information is sent to the instructor via internet
and a required action is to be made by them.

  Detects safety of workers under inconsistent/unsafe climatic conditions like construction sites,factories,etc.
